reviewText: It's BABYMETAL, what else do you need to know!? Buy it!

Babymetal concerts are the best so having them on Blu-ray is super. It came fast and the concerts on it are outstanding. If you love metal and love Japanese then you will love these three wonderful young ladies.
Babymetal does it agen, great sound , great moves and over all a beautiful  video I will watch over and over..  2 shows with a new song.
